<http://www.spektrix.com/tidemarktheatre/event/50401ARMBCNTPHTPBVLQSVDRCMHSBBNBM>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Open Up Your Whole Heart";
  schema:description """
	You are invited to join Discovery Singers for their spring performance on Saturday, April 18, 2026!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Campbell River United Church<span><br/></span>Saturday, April 18, 2026<span><br/></span>Show at 6:30pm (doors at 6:00pm)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>“Open Up Your Whole Heart” will feature contemporary music encouraging you to let go, to be vulnerable, and embrace the future. You will hear popular songs from artists like Natasha Bedingfield, The Staves, Billy Joel, I’m With Her and many more.<span><br/></span>Featuring local trio Mood Swings, and musical guests Lauren Miller & Sarah Olsen, Discovery Singers will be joined by their wonderful band:<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><ul><li> Corijn de Roo, percussion</li><li> Keith Goddard, guitar</li><li> Dylan Gordan, bass</li><li> Tim Petkau, piano</li></ul><span><br/></span>Last year’s winter events sold out quickly and we listened! Discovery Singers are excited to be sharing their program with you at a larger venue…but don’t wait too long to get your tickets, this show will be the perfect concert to kickstart your spring season.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Tickets: $20 <span class=\"ItalicText\">(+applicable fees)</span>
""";
