<http://www.spektrix.com/tidemarktheatre/event/53401ABPVVPPBPJCQVLMKKHHLLVGLBJJB>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Pride at the Tide";
  schema:description """
	Join us for a night of drag, funk, and community at the Tidemark Theatre. Come as you are, bring your people (or just yourself), and be part of a shared celebration.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The night features Vancouver icon <span class=\"BoldText\">Peach Cobblah</span> - a performer, creator, and longtime force in the queer arts scene. Known for her sharp wit and commanding presence, Peach brings humour and heart to the stage.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Celestial Seasons</span> co-hosts the evening, bringing glamour and an interactive performance style shaped by global influences.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>And by popular demand, headlining the night… <span class=\"BoldText\">Queer As Funk!</span><span><br/></span>This beloved Vancouver collective blends funk, soul, and Motown into a full-on dance party. With powerhouse vocals, a tight horn section, and an infectious groove, they turn every show into a space where people can connect, move, and celebrate together.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Whether you’re attending with friends, family, or flying solo, you are welcome here.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Tickets:$28.00 Members/Students, $33.00 Non-Members <span class=\"ItalicText\">(+applicable taxes & fees)</span>
""";
