  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Snotty Nose Rez Kids ";
  schema:description """
	Snotty Nose Rez Kids are back! Fresh off a JUNO nomination for Rap Single of the Year, Yung Trybez and Young D return to the Tidemark with a live show that that continues to draw audiences across Canada and beyond.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>From breakout tracks like <span class=\"ItalicText\">Boujee Natives</span> to Polaris Prize shortlists, major award wins, and a recent signing with Sony Music, SNRK have built their career on their own terms. Their music combines sharp lyricism, humour, lived experience, and hits hardest in a live show setting.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Known for their incredible live shows, this all ages performance offers a rare chance to see Snotty Nose Rez Kids in a space open to everyone.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Their last Tidemark appearance sold out. Advance tickets strongly recommended.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Tickets: $38.00 Members/Students/First Nation Community, $43.00 Non-members <span class=\"ItalicText\">(+applicable taxes & fees)</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://purchase.tidemarktheatre.com/EventAvailability?EventId=40201\">Limited VIP add-on for $60 (+applicable taxes &amp; fees) includes meet &amp; greet and photo opportunity after the show!</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">** You MUST have a ticket for the performance to access the Meet & Greet</span></span>
""";
