<http://www.spektrix.com/tidemarktheatre/event/52201AGLBQNPLVLHRQSQHGRRPVTMJCMCR>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Spark, Shadow and Shimmer";
  schema:description """
	Quadra Island Festival of Chamber Music was founded in 2011, and provides Islanders with a week of exquisite music performed by international-renowned musicians.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">SPARK, SHADOW and SHIMMER: </span><span class=\"BoldText\">Friday, June 26th  7:00 pm </span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Quadra Community Centre</span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\"> </span>W.A. Mozart: Quintet in C Major for two violins, two violas and cello <span><br/></span>Max Bruch: Selections from Eight Pieces for viola, clarinet and piano<span><br/></span>Maurice Ravel: <span class=\"ItalicText\">Introduction & Allegro</span> for harp and ensemble<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Tickets: $25.00 Admission <span class=\"ItalicText\">(+applicable taxes & fees)</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>For more information on the exceptional talent playing this year's festival and photos from last years performances, please visit <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.quadrafestival.ca/\">https://www.quadrafestival.ca/</a>
""";
