<http://www.spektrix.com/tidemarktheatre/event/52401AGHHMCQSLMQHGTNTVGPTNHJMVRQM>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Stealing Dan";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">Stealing Dan</span> is widely recognized as an ultra-authentic homage to Steely Dan, faithfully recreating the sophisticated arrangements, tonal character, and studio precision of the original recordings. The group delivers a true-to-form replication that captures the artistry and excellence of one of the most influential pop-jazz bands of all time.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Audiences can expect to hear Steely Dan’s most celebrated hits, including <span class=\"ItalicText\">Reeling In The Years, Peg, Josie, FM, Hey Nineteen, My Old School, Black Cow </span>alongside select deep-track favourites cherished by devoted fans.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Stealing Dan promises an evening of extraordinary musicianship and timeless music, offering audiences in Campbell River a rare chance to experience the Steely Dan sound brought to life on stage.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>\"Stealing Dan truly embodies the sound and precision of Steely Dan”<span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Joelle Rabu – Nanaimo International Jazz Festival</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>“Stealing Dan was without any doubt, the surprise hit of the festival<span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Susan Wood – Vancouver Island MusicFest / Director Marketing & Media</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>“We <span class=\"ItalicText\">never </span>have back-to-back repeat performers at our events, but Stealing Dan was the exception.  Absolutely superb!”<span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">John Donnelly – Filberg Festival / V.P. MRG Concert Productions</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">And a few comments from our on-line fans from around the world:</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>* What kind of black magic is this? Nobody can sound that close to Steely Dan!<span><br/></span>* If I wasn't looking, I'd SWEAR it was Steely Dan!<span><br/></span>* This band absolutely nailed it!!!<span><br/></span>* Superb..as close as it gets<span><br/></span>* Best cover of Steely Dan ever heard<span><br/></span>* Stellar. To hear how close this group is to the original is the boys is spooky!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCWkEDHRxN-NyBKk427LFAjw\">To hear this extraordinary band, click here</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Tickets: $40.00 Admission <span class=\"ItalicText\">(+applicable taxes & fees)</span>
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-05-30T19:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
  schema:image <https://system.spektrix.com/tidemarktheatre/files/a6e67e47-9fb5-48ef-905b-9c75c3709574.jpg>;
  schema:location <https://spektrix.com/tidemarktheatre/location/405AGDKDKNLGVLJCSNTLQBVTRTGBTHCPJ>;
  schema:url <https://tidemarktheatre.com/event/stealing-dan/>;
  schema:offers _:27f0623284aa408d9fe9a7f2081ff7887166;
  schema:duration "PT120M";
  schema:endDate "2026-05-30T21:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime .

